  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped carrots and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, and salt, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the red lentils, water, and pink food coloring, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes, or until the lentils are al-dente.",
    "Stir in the chopped peanuts and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Serve the pilaf hot, garnished with additional peanuts if desired."
